<p>The Ra’ Takakhan system was founded as part of Colonia’s move to economic self-sufficiency by the Ra’ Takakhan Resources Inc organisation – a democratic feudal body loosely modelled on the Knights of Colonial Karma.</p>
<p>One of the smaller orbital extraction facilities, it produces a wide range of ores and precious metals (especially Silver) for the many nearby refineries. In mid-3304 a Civilian Installation was constructed to provide high quality accommodation for the miners, making this one of the more popular postings.</p>
<p>The LWY-129 bulk cargo ship makes it’s final mining stop of its circuit at this system, before transferring the ores to Luchtaine’s nearby refineries.</p>
